A Kenya Defence Forces (KDF soldier based in Embakasi, Nairobi has been charged with defilement before a Nyeri court.
The soldier, Martin Kabura, denied two counts of defiling a 16-year old relative on January 5, 2020 with the promise that he would help her secure a place at a girls’ school in Othaya.



